title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Mar 7 2022

description:
Breaking down where we can get oil. Are the American people willing to wreck the economy to combat the Russian invasion of Ukraine? Karol Markowicz piece in NY Post agrees with C&B: Demand covid apologies from leaders who were dead wrong. CDC director admits they over-promised on vaccine effectiveness, doesn't apologize. C&B take calls on rising prices and Ukraine.
